      "writtenOn": "2017-08-19T18:34:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I expected anything with \"ForTesting\" on it to be used for testing the internal implementation details of the package. I don\u0027t see that (yet). Even so, should this be clearForTesting so that it\u0027s only accessible to the same package?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 42,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 42,
        "endChar": 20
      },
      "revId": "286a109cb982d4ad87a4fb8c338a071f00b99744",
